                            </FooterDetails>
                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>Rules and regulations that are associated with the Executive
                                Office of the President are codified in the first chapter, sections
                                100–199, of 3 CFR.</Paragraph>
                        </Detail>
                    </Details>
